pretix-description =
    pretix is a self-hosted, open-source event ticketing and registration platform.

    It provides a full-featured online shop for event tickets, workshop registrations,
    and merchandise. pretix supports flexible pricing rules, discount vouchers, waiting
    lists, seating plans, and multiple payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal, bank transfer).
    Mobile check-in apps are available for iOS and Android.

pretix-features =
    - Online shop for tickets and registrations
    - Flexible pricing, discounts, and vouchers
    - Waiting lists and capacity management
    - Seating plan support
    - Multiple payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal, bank transfer)
    - Mobile check-in apps (iOS and Android)
    - Multi-event and organizer support
    - PostgreSQL-backed
    - REST API for integrations
